04:22.147 --> 04:24.114
Never mind.

04:24.116 --> 04:25.849
Hey, so I was thinking
you know,

04:25.851 --> 04:27.583
the fair is in town
this weekend.

04:27.585 --> 04:29.251
What do say we all go
over tomorrow afternoon?

04:29.253 --> 04:31.353
We can grab some rides,
have some cotton candy.

04:31.355 --> 04:32.589
What do you think?
My treat.

04:32.591 --> 04:34.357
