to be late.

05:10.630 --> 05:12.963
- Lunch number 1.
- Thanks.

05:12.965 --> 05:14.398
Lunch number 2.

05:14.400 --> 05:15.633
Bye, Mom. Bye, Dad.

05:15.635 --> 05:16.967
Bye.

05:16.969 --> 05:18.604
- Love you!
- You, too.

05:20.140 --> 05:22.641
I have to turn this in on time
or I won't get an A.

05:22.643 --> 05:24.577
Don't worry, you'll be fine.

05:47.667 --> 05:50.101
I think that math test
literally fried my brains.

05:50.103 --> 05:51.670
It could have been in German

05:51.672 --> 05:53.572
and I still would probably get
the same grade.

05:53.574 --> 05:55.340
- It wasn't that bad.
- Says you.

05:55.342 --> 05:57.210
- What?
