11:30.188 --> 11:35.292
<i>♪ Can you feel it
In the air? ♪</i>

11:35.294 --> 11:41.200
<i>♪ We're all the same
Disciples ♪</i>

11:50.309 --> 11:52.642
Hey, one of your
headlights is out.

11:52.644 --> 11:55.145
Oh, yeah, I know.
I've been meaning to fix that.

11:55.147 --> 11:56.681
It takes
like five minutes to fix.

11:56.683 --> 11:58.649
Well, I procrastinate
on some things.

11:58.651 --> 12:00.016
You mean your life?

12:00.018 --> 12:03.054
Oh, don't be a smart-ass,
come on.

12:03.056 --> 12:04.589
Reminds me though,
remember that game

12:04.591 --> 12:05.990
we used to play
when you were a kid

12:05.992 --> 12:08.259
where you're drivin' along
and see a car

12:08.261 --> 12:10.828
with a headlight out,
do you remember?

12:10.830 --> 12:13.564
No, no, no, God.

12:13.566 --> 12:15.166
Th... cut that's cheating,
come on.

12:15.168 --> 12:16.866
No, it's not.
Those are your rules!

12:16.868 --> 12:18.669
Oh, that's cheating.

12:18.671 --> 12:20.204
- God.
- You're just mad I won.

12:20.206 --> 12:21.906
Oh, okay.

12:23.544 --> 12:24.676
What's all this about?

12:24.678 --> 12:26.811
- You'll see.
- Okay.

12:26.813 --> 12:28.582
Just be patient,
just another second.

12:29.683 --> 12:31.350
Alright.

12:31.352 --> 12:33.085
Prepare yourself.

12:33.087 --> 12:35.586
What am I lookin' at?

12:35.588 --> 12:39.190
Say "hello" to Spanky.

12:39.192 --> 12:42.694
Oh, oh. Hi, Spanky.

12:44.365 --> 12:46.734
- I know. Isn't he cute?
- Hi, buddy.

12:48.469 --> 12:49.901
Dad, why are we here?

12:49.903 --> 12:52.705
I thought you'd enjoy this,
just the two of us.

12:52.707 --> 12:53.805
And Spanky.

12:53.807 --> 12:54.808
And Spanky.

12:56.110 --> 12:58.077
- Is he yours?
- He sure is.

12:58.079 --> 12:59.378
When did you get him?

12:59.380 --> 13:01.748
I got him a couple
of months ago.

13:01.750 --> 13:03.716
My friend Matt couldn't
take care of him anymore,

13:03.718 --> 13:06.519
asked if I'd help out,
and I said, "Sure".

13:06.521 --> 13:08.288
Well, that was
really nice of you.

13:08.290 --> 13:10.590
Well, they take really
good care of him here.

13:10.592 --> 13:12.892
At least, they will
till the end of the month.

13:12.894 --> 13:14.162
Oh, it's just for a month?

13:16.097 --> 13:17.432
I'll think of something.

13:19.034 --> 13:21.868
I know you think
I'm irresponsible.

13:21.870 --> 13:24.637
And I guess
I do some crazy stuff.

13:24.639 --> 13:26.441
I mean I got a miniature horse,
right?

13:28.043 --> 13:29.911
I don't think
you're irresponsible.

13:31.112 --> 13:35.048
Well, I know I do some

13:35.050 --> 13:37.251
random things in my life,

13:37.253 --> 13:42.323
but you, Addy,
are my anchor.

13:42.325 --> 13:45.959
You're the only thing
that keeps me centered at all.

13:45.961 --> 13:47.994
If you weren't around,
I'd have no place

13:47.996 --> 13:50.232
to always come back to.

13:53.869 --> 13:55.304
You might be a little crazy...

13:56.339 --> 13:58.305
...but you're my dad.

13:58.307 --> 14:00.941
You're like the most
important person in my world.

14:00.943 --> 14:02.109
Oh!

14:02.111 --> 14:03.445
Well, you and Mom.

14:03.447 --> 14:05.315
And Ella,
when she's not being annoying.

14:07.150 --> 14:09.050
You give this to Spanky

14:09.052 --> 14:11.253
and I'm gonna give this
to you.

14:12.388 --> 14:14.589
I made this for you.

14:14.591 --> 14:16.424
I know you kids
don't do CDs anymore,

14:16.426 --> 14:17.958
but that's how I roll.

14:17.960 --> 14:19.160
What's on it?

14:19.162 --> 14:21.363
Just some stuff
I've been working on.

14:21.365 --> 14:24.802
And the best of it,
you were the inspiration for.

14:26.370 --> 14:27.369
Thanks, Dad.

14:27.371 --> 14:29.372
Oh.

14:29.374 --> 14:31.207
Thank you, princess.

14:31.209 --> 14:33.976
Okay, let's put Spanky up
and go get some food, okay?

14:33.978 --> 14:35.510
- I'm starving.
- Alright, okay.

14:38.982 --> 14:40.616
I just wanted you
to meet Spanky.

14:40.618 --> 14:41.684
He's adorable, right?

14:41.686 --> 14:43.219
- Yeah.
- Okay.

14:43.221 --> 14:44.720
- Bye, Spanky.
- Bye, buddy.

14:44.722 --> 14:46.655
Yeah, okay,
I'll come see you tomorrow.

14:46.657 --> 14:48.859
Good boy.

14:48.861 --> 14:50.294
Alright.

15:07.912 --> 15:09.912
Thought you were
getting back early.

15:09.914 --> 15:11.548
I know, I'm sorry.

15:11.550 --> 15:13.116
Traffic was bad
on the way back.

15:13.118 --> 15:15.786
Always something with you,
isn't it, Robert?

15:15.788 --> 15:17.755
Mom, that's enough.

15:17.757 --> 15:19.456
It's fine.

15:19.458 --> 15:20.424
Goodnight, Dad.

15:20.426 --> 15:21.659
Goodnight, baby.

15:21.661 --> 15:23.729
- I love you.
- I love you, princess.

15:28.400 --> 15:29.766
I'm sorry to be on edge,

15:29.768 --> 15:32.068
but things are
a little tight around here.

15:32.070 --> 15:34.204
Addy needs new shoes,
a backpack...

15:34.206 --> 15:35.773
I thought James
was doing great.

15:35.775 --> 15:39.677
Well, it's hard! He just started
his own business.

15:39.679 --> 15:41.546
I'll make sure
to send you a check

15:41.548 --> 15:43.281
as soon as I get back
from the festival.

15:43.283 --> 15:45.550
It's not just about a check,
Robert.

15:45.552 --> 15:47.451
She's your daughter,
not James'.

15:47.453 --> 15:51.925
Could we... could we please talk
about this on Tuesday, okay?

15:53.959 --> 15:55.829
Please don't
disappoint her again.

15:57.163 --> 15:58.097
Yes, ma'am.

15:59.733 --> 16:01.600
You don't always have
to treat him this way, you know.

16:01.602 --> 16:03.134
Addy, go to bed.

16:03.136 --> 16:05.904
I know you hate him,
but he's trying, okay?

16:05.906 --> 16:07.239
I don't hate him.

16:07.241 --> 16:08.607
Yeah?

16:08.609 --> 16:10.812
You got a really funny way
of showing it then.

16:16.784 --> 16:21.422
- What was that?
- Nothing. Just Addy being Addy.

17:17.046 --> 17:19.413
Hey, what's up?

17:19.415 --> 17:21.550
<i>You're gonna love this,
check your email.</i>

17:21.551 --> 17:22.486
Okay.

17:25.021 --> 17:29.557
