17:33.964 --> 17:35.564
Where did you get this?

17:35.566 --> 17:37.899
<i>He just posted it
on Instagram.</i>

17:37.901 --> 17:39.968
Oh, what are you
like stalking now?

17:39.970 --> 17:42.904
<i>Come on,
I'm doing this for you, Ads.</i>

17:45.309 --> 17:47.010
