18:31.390 --> 18:32.725
I'm so sorry.

18:38.196 --> 18:39.330
No.

18:41.432 --> 18:42.568
No.

18:44.637 --> 18:46.572
Mom.

20:23.106 --> 20:25.739
Well, Robert never remarried

20:25.741 --> 20:27.507
and didn't have other children,

20:27.509 --> 20:31.145
so the next of kin is you,
Addy.

20:31.147 --> 20:33.683
And w... what does this
all mean exactly?

20:34.916 --> 20:37.317
Well, let's see.

20:37.319 --> 20:42.189
Uh, there is a guitar
signed by various rock artists.

20:42.191 --> 20:45.358
Uh, then there is an original
collection of records,

20:45.360 --> 20:47.530
as well as a vintage
record player.

20:49.365 --> 20:55.706
Uh, there's a checking account
in the balance of $828.92

20:59.509 --> 21:02.779
And lastly,
there is Robert's horse.

21:04.947 --> 21:07.381
- He's given me Spanky?
- What... who's Spanky?

21:07.383 --> 21:09.251
Yes, there is a horse

21:09.253 --> 21:11.620
in Robert's possession
named "Spanky".

21:11.622 --> 21:13.588
Uh, also
one-way transportation costs

21:13.590 --> 21:17.425
have been paid,
along with a bucket of oats

21:17.427 --> 21:20.129
- and a couple of bales of hay.
- Excuse me.

21:20.131 --> 21:22.231
Excuse me,
excuse me, a horse?

21:22.233 --> 21:25.399
Like a... like a real...

21:25.401 --> 21:27.469
Like a... um, horse?

21:27.471 --> 21:29.304
Yes, sir.

21:29.306 --> 21:31.907
Is it legal to keep a horse
in the suburbs?

21:31.909 --> 21:34.243
- He's a miniature horse, James.
- Miniature, okay.

21:34.245 --> 21:36.645
What does it cost to feed
and board a horse?

21:36.647 --> 21:38.480
Does it say in the... in the
will, what it... What it costs?

21:38.482 --> 21:40.249
Is there an instruction manual?

21:40.251 --> 21:42.552
Honey, I think right now
we need to focus

21:42.554 --> 21:47.823
on Robert's wishes
and bring the horse here

21:47.825 --> 21:51.594
until we can figure out
something more suitable for him.

21:51.596 --> 21:53.698
Keep him in the back...
in the backyard?

21:58.336 --> 21:59.704
Alright. Alrighty, then.

22:01.841 --> 22:03.374
So Spanky's ours now?

22:05.010 --> 22:06.579
Technically, he's yours.

22:11.816 --> 22:13.885
So Spanky, huh?

22:15.020 --> 22:15.921
Yep.

22:18.157 --> 22:19.357
That's a funny name.

22:21.460 --> 22:22.828
When did your dad
get a horse?

22:23.863 --> 22:25.462
Like a couple of months ago.

22:25.464 --> 22:27.531
Why?

22:27.533 --> 22:30.168
I don't know. His friend
gave it to him or something.

22:30.170 --> 22:31.669
Enough with the questions.

22:31.671 --> 22:32.772
Okay.

22:44.818 --> 22:47.051
Leave it to Robert
to do something so random.

22:47.053 --> 22:50.655
I still don't know
how he got a horse.

22:50.657 --> 22:52.191
What are we
supposed to do now?

22:52.193 --> 22:53.558
I have no clue.

22:53.560 --> 22:57.029
I'm going over our finances
and it is bad.

22:57.031 --> 23:00.464
We're not gonna be able
to keep this horse for long.

23:00.466 --> 23:02.502
Well, like we have
to figure something out.

23:27.395 --> 23:29.261
We're so sorry, Addy.

23:29.263 --> 23:32.234
If there is anything you need,
let us know.

23:35.270 --> 23:36.238
We're here for you.

24:04.533 --> 24:07.001
Hey, you're home late.

24:07.003 --> 24:09.305
Yeah, I just had to clear
my mind a little bit.

24:10.739 --> 24:14.141
Look. Dally can totally give
a high five now.

24:14.143 --> 24:16.143
Good girl!

24:16.145 --> 24:17.610
So cool, isn't it?

24:17.612 --> 24:20.049
Yes, it's very cool.

24:23.853 --> 24:26.355
Hey, do you maybe
wanna hang out with us?

24:26.357 --> 24:28.290
I could show you
some more tricks.

24:28.292 --> 24:31.760
Listen, Ella, I know you're just
trying to help and everything,

24:31.762 --> 24:35.162
but I just need
some space, okay?

24:35.164 --> 24:36.998
Sure.

24:37.000 --> 24:39.135
Alright,
I'm gonna go to my room now.

25:45.838 --> 25:48.907
I am the pancake king!

25:53.245 --> 25:55.245
Hi.

25:55.247 --> 25:56.182
You're up early.

25:58.250 --> 25:59.716
Wow!

25:59.718 --> 26:02.653
Nice um, pancakes.

26:02.655 --> 26:04.556
Yeah.

26:04.558 --> 26:07.861
I wanted to uh, surprise you
with one of my famous designs.

26:16.269 --> 26:18.602
I know it's hard, Addy.

26:18.604 --> 26:20.271
- Do you?
- I do.

26:20.273 --> 26:23.808
My mom died
when I was about your age.

26:23.810 --> 26:24.744
Oh.

26:25.946 --> 26:27.313
Um, I didn't know that.

26:27.315 --> 26:29.482
No, it's okay.
I don't usually talk about it.

26:29.484 --> 26:31.283
It all happened really fast.

26:31.285 --> 26:35.088
She got sick, and then a few
months later, she was gone.

26:36.289 --> 26:37.691
I'm really sorry, James.

26:39.292 --> 26:41.993
I remember feeling
very withdrawn,

26:41.995 --> 26:43.598
very angry.

26:45.299 --> 26:46.267
Yeah.

26:48.302 --> 26:49.802
Anyway... Ahem.

26:49.804 --> 26:52.104
My mom was
a really good baker,

26:52.106 --> 26:56.243
so now anytime I bake,
I think about her.

26:56.245 --> 26:58.878
So she's gone, but uh...

26:58.880 --> 27:00.579
...she's here whenever I want.

27:00.581 --> 27:02.548
Did she use to make pancakes
like these?

27:02.550 --> 27:04.451
Like these? No.
No, that's all me.

27:04.453 --> 27:06.919
I got to say I think
I crushed these this morning.

27:06.921 --> 27:08.255
Might be my masterpiece.

27:08.257 --> 27:09.857
I almost don't want you
to eat 'em.

27:11.126 --> 27:12.461
You know,
maybe there's something...

27:13.795 --> 27:18.131
...fun that would remind you
of your dad.

27:18.133 --> 27:19.166
Like what?

27:19.168 --> 27:21.034
Could be music.

27:21.036 --> 27:22.238
No.

27:23.771 --> 27:26.139
Every time I hear
one of his songs, I cry.

27:26.141 --> 27:27.340
So...

27:27.342 --> 27:29.209
Did Robert bake?

27:29.211 --> 27:30.477
I don't think so.

27:30.479 --> 27:32.380
Yeah, well, you know,
I'm out of ideas,

27:32.382 --> 27:35.550
but something fun,
something crazy.

27:35.552 --> 27:37.886
It's gonna be up to you
to find out what that is.

27:39.222 --> 27:40.590
Thanks, James.

27:42.392 --> 27:46.793
You
are most welcome, my lady.

27:59.209 --> 28:01.175
You're a cute little horse,
aren't you?

28:04.381 --> 28:06.317
Some surprise Dad left me.

28:08.419 --> 28:11.385
I read online
that horses like carrots.

28:11.387 --> 28:13.424
Do you like carrots?

28:17.394 --> 28:18.529
Dang! Ha, ha.

28:21.031 --> 28:22.731
Wow!

28:22.733 --> 28:24.301
You sure do.

28:27.405 --> 28:29.274
Hmm, let's try something.

28:32.077 --> 28:33.311
You follow me?

28:34.411 --> 28:35.744
Come here.

28:41.686 --> 28:43.954
Alright, let's go over here.

28:45.756 --> 28:48.191
Good job!

28:48.193 --> 28:49.826
Alright, now this way.

28:49.828 --> 28:51.995
Good!

28:51.997 --> 28:53.365
And this way.

28:58.436 --> 29:00.238
Alright, one more time.
Come again.

29:03.408 --> 29:06.443
You did so good!

29:06.445 --> 29:07.380
Another one?

29:12.618 --> 29:13.751
You cleaned me out.

29:13.753 --> 29:15.919
They're all gone.

29:49.155 --> 29:51.222
Hey, what's up?

29:51.224 --> 29:53.124
Can I talk to you
about something?

29:53.126 --> 29:54.795
Sure. Come on in.

29:57.898 --> 29:58.932
Talk to me.

30:01.502 --> 30:05.504
I know it's been really hard
on Addy since her dad died.

30:05.506 --> 30:07.306
I've been trying
to be nice to her,

30:07.308 --> 30:10.642
but it's just really hard.

30:10.644 --> 30:14.012
- I feel like she hates me.
- No, honey.

30:14.014 --> 30:15.781
She doesn't hate you.

30:15.783 --> 30:19.685
She just is going through
a really hard time.

30:19.687 --> 30:23.189
But I think she's starting
to feel a little better.

30:23.191 --> 30:24.523
How do you know that?

30:24.525 --> 30:27.126
Well, I saw her today
with Spanky.

30:27.128 --> 30:29.128
And I think
he's good for her.

30:29.130 --> 30:32.064
You know how Dally makes you
feel better when you're sad?

30:32.066 --> 30:33.400
Hmm.

30:33.402 --> 30:35.436
That's what Spanky
is doing for Addy.

30:38.072 --> 30:41.340
I just wish Addy and I could be
friends again.

30:41.342 --> 30:43.577
- Like before.
- Yeah, well,

30:43.579 --> 30:46.213
some of that has to do
with growing up.

30:46.215 --> 30:47.913
But it will get better,
I promise.

30:47.915 --> 30:50.050
And in the meantime,

30:50.052 --> 30:54.491
the only thing you can do
is be a good sister to her.

30:59.994 --> 31:02.064
- Thanks, Mom.
- Anytime.

31:04.233 --> 31:05.934
- Love you.
- Love you, too.

31:20.718 --> 31:21.719
I made you something.

31:22.918 --> 31:24.487
Oh, thanks, Ella.

31:26.589 --> 31:27.889
Mmm.

31:27.891 --> 31:29.690
I haven't had this
in like forever.

31:29.692 --> 31:31.192
Remember when we had

31:31.194 --> 31:33.528
- that chugging contest when we were little?
- Yeah.

31:33.530 --> 31:35.464
And we had to stay home
from school the whole day,

31:35.466 --> 31:36.632
'cause we were so sick.

31:36.634 --> 31:38.534
I know!
You had like eight glasses.

31:38.536 --> 31:39.601
I had nine.

31:39.603 --> 31:40.602
I beat you by one.

31:40.604 --> 31:42.037
Mom was so mad.

31:42.039 --> 31:43.439
Yeah, she was.

31:43.441 --> 31:45.607
What are you looking at?

31:45.609 --> 31:47.876
I'm doing some
research on horse training.

31:47.878 --> 31:50.412
Spanky really likes carrots,
so I'm gonna use those

31:50.414 --> 31:52.614
- and get him to do stuff.
- Like what?

31:52.616 --> 31:55.617
I don't know. That's what
I'm trying to figure out.

31:55.619 --> 31:57.619
I wanna get Dally
to do some new tricks.

31:57.621 --> 32:01.658
- Like roll over, play dead, and things like that.
- Hmm.

32:01.660 --> 32:04.193
Do you think I could watch you
train Spanky sometime?

32:04.195 --> 32:06.296
Yeah, I'm actually
gonna go outside right now.

32:06.298 --> 32:08.198
- Do you wanna come?
- I'd love that.

32:08.200 --> 32:10.632
- Okay, cool. Bring Dally.
- Dally.

32:10.634 --> 32:13.402
- Come here, girl.
- Dally?

32:13.404 --> 32:14.804
Dally?

32:14.806 --> 32:16.972
She must be around here
somewhere.

32:16.974 --> 32:19.642
Where did she go?

32:19.644 --> 32:20.679
Dally?

32:33.192 --> 32:34.924
Uh, is your dog
lying on my pony?

32:34.926 --> 32:36.061
I think so.

32:38.497 --> 32:39.496
But how?

32:39.498 --> 32:41.066
I have no idea.

32:43.268 --> 32:44.502
- Hey, girl.
- Hey, guys.

32:44.504 --> 32:46.370
How did you get up here?

32:46.372 --> 32:48.706
I don't know about you,
but I think this is pretty cool.

32:48.708 --> 32:50.307
I know.

32:50.309 --> 32:52.746
I've never seen a dog
on top of a horse before.

32:54.681 --> 32:57.482
You think she'll stay
if Spanky starts walking around?

32:57.484 --> 33:00.620
I mean there's only one way
to find out, right?

33:04.590 --> 33:06.290
Hold on!

33:06.292 --> 33:08.192
Come on, Spanky!

33:08.194 --> 33:11.363
She's doing it!
Dally's riding Spanky!

33:11.365 --> 33:12.964
Come here.

33:12.966 --> 33:15.300
- Good jo... oh, cute!
- Are you getting this?

33:15.302 --> 33:17.102
Oh yeah!

33:17.104 --> 33:18.703
Good job, guys!

33:18.705 --> 33:20.305
You did so good!

33:21.809 --> 33:23.542
Alright, should we go
and do more research?

33:23.544 --> 33:24.709
Yeah.

33:24.711 --> 33:25.877
Come on, Dally.

33:25.879 --> 33:27.812
Here, girl.

33:27.814 --> 33:28.813
Come on.

33:28.815 --> 33:30.183
Yay!

33:34.856 --> 33:36.691
Aren't you gonna
come look at this?

33:41.429 --> 33:43.931
Why don't I take it from here?

33:43.933 --> 33:45.199
Okay.

33:48.535 --> 33:49.804
Dally.

33:56.177 --> 33:57.911
Sit.

33:57.913 --> 33:59.312
Good girl!

33:59.314 --> 34:00.716
Okay.

34:02.751 --> 34:03.919
Okay, down.

34:06.154 --> 34:09.523
Awesome. Good job, Dally.

34:09.525 --> 34:10.656
Come on, girl.

34:10.658 --> 34:12.091
Come on. Roll over.

34:12.092 --> 34:13.860
You can do it.

34:13.862 --> 34:15.896
Keep it coming.

34:15.898 --> 34:19.032
Good girl. Amazing, Dally!

34:19.034 --> 34:22.668
See? Even your little sister
can teach you a few things.

34:22.670 --> 34:24.170
Okay, Professor Dunham.

34:24.172 --> 34:25.708
- We gonna do this or what?
- Ha, ha.

34:29.110 --> 34:30.545
Look!

34:30.547 --> 34:33.947
Good girl!
Here you go, here you go!

34:33.949 --> 34:34.850
Yeah.

34:40.289 --> 34:41.791
Hey.

34:43.793 --> 34:45.695
- Oh, bring it.
- Oh!

34:46.795 --> 34:48.663
Go get it. Go.

34:48.665 --> 34:50.431
Yay, girl!

34:50.433 --> 34:52.300
Come on, bring it. Bring it.

34:52.302 --> 34:53.802
Right.

34:53.804 --> 34:55.039
Here.

35:00.744 --> 35:02.143
Come here. Bring it back.

35:02.145 --> 35:04.748
- Bring it... please!
- Come back.

35:07.051 --> 35:08.984
Give it back!

35:08.986 --> 35:10.755
Give it to me.

35:17.428 --> 35:18.863
Drop it.

35:30.841 --> 35:33.411
What is it doing?

35:40.052 --> 35:41.386
Good girl.

35:46.824 --> 35:48.290
Oh!

35:48.292 --> 35:49.193
Oh!

35:56.068 --> 35:58.001
Yay!

35:58.003 --> 35:59.538
Oh!

36:01.740 --> 36:03.373
Dally, load up.

36:03.375 --> 36:04.642
- Yay!
- Yeah!

36:04.644 --> 36:05.812
Good!

36:12.818 --> 36:14.153
What are you doing?

36:26.365 --> 36:27.631
How about when Spanky
was running

36:27.633 --> 36:29.167
and Dally was staying on
perfectly?

36:29.169 --> 36:31.636
He was going pretty fast, too.
I mean it was awesome.

36:31.638 --> 36:34.004
Who has seen a dog
ride a horse before?

36:34.006 --> 36:35.406
I certainly haven't.

36:35.408 --> 36:37.675
- Me neither.
- You know what we should do?

36:37.677 --> 36:39.211
We should make
an Instagram account for them

36:39.213 --> 36:40.611
and we should call it, um...

36:40.613 --> 36:41.779
A Dog and Pony Show.

36:41.781 --> 36:43.682
- Yes!
- I'll make it right now.

36:43.684 --> 36:45.550
I'll post some photos
and videos from today.

36:45.552 --> 36:46.618
Perfect.

36:46.620 --> 36:48.053
Now, which one of you two

36:48.055 --> 36:50.223
- taught Dally to ride Spanky?
- Neither of us.

36:50.225 --> 36:52.524
We just walked outside
and Dally was lying on Spanky.

36:52.526 --> 36:53.827
Crazy, right?

36:55.063 --> 36:56.195
Brilliant!

36:57.931 --> 36:59.363
What?

36:59.365 --> 37:00.834
Oh, Dad!

37:03.303 --> 37:04.770
James?

37:04.772 --> 37:05.839
Yes, honey?

37:10.779 --> 37:11.880
What is it?

37:14.682 --> 37:17.784
I'm really happy that the girls
are having so much fun

37:17.786 --> 37:19.519
with Dally and Spanky.

37:19.521 --> 37:21.556
I think Addy's
getting better...

37:22.957 --> 37:24.957
But...

37:24.959 --> 37:27.460
But I don't think
we can keep Spanky.

37:27.462 --> 37:28.928
You've seen our bank account.

37:28.930 --> 37:30.930
We can't afford a horse.

37:30.932 --> 37:33.133
Look, I get it.

37:33.135 --> 37:35.803
Addy's dad gave her Spanky
and I don't want her to think

37:35.805 --> 37:38.471
we're being insensitive
about that.

37:38.473 --> 37:42.142
But I do think I've found
a place where Spanky can go.

37:42.144 --> 37:44.611
- Really?
- Hmm.

37:44.613 --> 37:46.512
Where?

37:46.514 --> 37:48.748
A guy who's
got a ranch up north,

37:48.750 --> 37:51.151
he's got plenty of space
for Spanky.

37:51.153 --> 37:52.786
We can come meet him whenever.

37:55.024 --> 37:57.457
I don't know
if we can do that to Addy.

37:57.459 --> 38:00.295
Maybe I can just pick up
an extra shift at the practice.

38:00.297 --> 38:03.932
You know that's
only a temporary solution.

38:03.934 --> 38:07.137
I know, but it's a start.

38:10.573 --> 38:12.005
You're right.

38:12.007 --> 38:13.740
And maybe if I close on one
of these houses soon,

38:13.742 --> 38:16.313
that will give us a little extra
breathing room, too.

38:17.814 --> 38:19.747
Thank you for being so good
about this.

38:19.749 --> 38:22.018
Anything
for you and the girls.

39:02.660 --> 39:03.761
Hey, Spanky.

39:05.197 --> 39:06.996
What are you doin' here?

39:06.998 --> 39:08.864
I mean it's been a long day.

39:08.866 --> 39:10.233
You're not too tired?

39:12.037 --> 39:13.171
Oh, is that so?

39:14.740 --> 39:16.406
I had a lot of fun with you,
too.

39:16.408 --> 39:18.543
And we'll keep doing it
for as long as we can.

39:20.846 --> 39:23.646
Alright, well,
I've gotta get some sleep.

39:23.648 --> 39:26.316
We'll work on more stuff
tomorrow. Okay?

39:26.318 --> 39:28.151
As soon as I get back
from school.

39:28.153 --> 39:29.886
Deal?

39:29.888 --> 39:31.755
Alright, deal.

39:31.757 --> 39:33.192
Goodnight, Spanky.

39:54.147 --> 39:56.881
This test was
certainly a mixed result.

39:56.883 --> 40:00.653
Some of you did well,
but a lot of you fell short.

40:11.664 --> 40:13.198
Guys, look at this.

40:13.200 --> 40:15.533
Okay, so we trained Dally
to jump up on Spanky.

40:15.535 --> 40:17.903
And all we have to do is point
to Spanky's back.

40:17.905 --> 40:20.205
And she jumps on his back
just like that?

40:20.207 --> 40:22.274
- Yeah, just like that.
- Cool.

40:22.276 --> 40:23.575
Okay, look at this one.

40:23.577 --> 40:25.744
So all I have to do
is walk over,

40:25.746 --> 40:28.149
and hold out a carrot,
and watch this.

40:31.419 --> 40:33.086
You guys should
totally enter them

40:33.088 --> 40:34.753
into the school talent show.

40:34.755 --> 40:36.054
The talent show?

40:36.056 --> 40:37.823
Yeah. It's coming up
in two weeks.

40:37.825 --> 40:40.926
The first prize is 1,000 bucks
and a bottomless ice cream bowl

40:40.928 --> 40:43.098
at Fifty-Five Flavors.

40:44.531 --> 40:46.099
Hmm.

40:46.101 --> 40:48.334
$1,000.

40:48.336 --> 40:51.840
But what if Spanky you know,
poops on stage?

40:53.174 --> 40:55.041
What are you
talking about?

40:55.043 --> 40:57.344
Horses take massive dumps
all the time.

40:57.346 --> 40:58.978
One time
when I was in New York,

40:58.980 --> 41:00.880
I was in the front seat
on a carriage ride,

41:00.882 --> 41:03.218
trust me, there were some things
you can't unsee.

41:04.686 --> 41:07.287
I think we'll be fine.

41:07.289 --> 41:09.789
Oh my God, I've been waiting
for this all day.

41:09.791 --> 41:12.126
I really wanna try out some
new stuff with Dally and Spanky.

41:12.128 --> 41:13.861
Yeah? Well, guess what?

41:13.863 --> 41:16.697
- Now we have a purpose.
- What do you mean?

41:16.699 --> 41:18.532
My school's talent show.

41:18.534 --> 41:20.534
I think we should enter
Dally and Spanky.

41:20.536 --> 41:23.203
